Yeah!

34
00:02:52,438 --> 00:02:55,642
Ordinary girls don't look as good in
an outfit like that as you do.

35
00:02:55,642 --> 00:02:58,711
You're the most suitable to deal with kids.

36
00:02:58,711 --> 00:03:00,180
What do you mean?

37
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:03,081
Your mental age is young and it's easy
for you to connect with kids.

38
00:03:03,716 --> 00:03:05,552
What the hell?!

39
00:03:05,552 --> 00:03:06,586
Jerk!

40
00:03:06,586 --> 00:03:07,787
Wait, Ryo!

41
00:03:07,787 --> 00:03:09,088
Are you going to run away from me?

42
00:03:09,088 --> 00:03:11,022
Stick to it!

43
